com.linecorp.armeria.client.encoding

Interface StreamDecoderFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DeflateStreamDecoderFactory, GzipStreamDecoderFactory

    public interface StreamDecoderFactory
    An interface that constructs a new StreamDecoder for a given Content-Encoding header value. A new decoder is valid for the lifetime of an HttpResponse.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String encodingHeaderValue()
      Returns the value of the Content-Encoding header which this factory applies to.
      StreamDecoder newDecoder()
      Construct a new StreamDecoder to use to decode an HttpResponse.
